{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2007-06-16",
 "title": "Return Under the Empire's Eye",
 "summary": "Years later, the cyborg-scarred Bazil McKenzie pilots his battered assault shuttle, the Dirty Jawa, out of hyperspace and blunders straight into an Imperial fleet guarding the planet Nelona. Rather than flee, he complies with the Star Destroyer Inquisitor's orders to halt and prepare for boarding, calmly presenting his papers to the inspecting lieutenant and troopers. Bazil truthfully explains he resigned from New Republic Intelligence and the Inner Council six years earlier, that his current allegiances are independent, and that he has come to reclaim property he once held in the Menrai district. Recounting his quiet recent life running a Tatooine orphanage and supporting his sister Jasmine Heretin's Corellian hospitals, he satisfies the lieutenant enough to be cleared to land under lockdown pending a background check, and the Dirty Jawa descends toward the spaceport.",
